1. If you're not already in the Data view, go there and change the data category for the Geographic Area Name to "State or Province"
2. Select the (empty) 2017 NAICS Footnote column and hide it from the report view
3. Navigate to the Report view and add a Map visual to the current page. Add Geographic Area Name as the Location and Number of employees as the Size
   Change the aggregation of Number of employees to "Average"

